the list of implemented task:
-----------------------------

fileset                 determine a list of files
mkdir                   create a directory/path
delete                  delete a file/directory
c-compile               compiles c files into object files
c-deps                  compiles dependencies for C files
java-compile            compiles java files into class files
gzip                    zips a file (gzip)
gunzip                  unzip a file (gzip)
touch                   updates a file's mod timestamp
file-type               return the type of a file
lib                     build static and dynamic libraries
tar                     creates (gnu) tar archives
untar                   extractes (gnu) tar archives
copy                    copies files and directories
clean                   cleans up a project area
link                    links object files and libraries to executables
objc-compile            objective c compile
filter                  filters a file and replaces placeholder
install                 install file/files
texinfo                 process texinfo files


additional functions:
---------------------
msg                     display all arguments (=echo)


